  "response": "Here are some popular dance club songs that have been well-received and are often played in clubs:\n\n1. **\"Levitating\" - Dua Lipa ft. DaBaby**\n2. **\"Don't Start Now\" - Dua Lipa**\n3. **\"Blinding Lights\" - The Weeknd**\n4. **\"Stay\" - The Kid LAROI & Justin Bieber**\n5. **\"Rain On Me\" - Lady Gaga & Ariana Grande**\n6. **\"Savage Love (Laxed - Siren Beat)\" - Jawsh 685 & Jason Derulo**\n7. **\"Head & Heart\" - Joel Corry ft. MNEK**\n8. **\"Roses (Imanbek Remix)\" - SAINt JHN**\n9. **\"Peaches\" - Justin Bieber ft. Daniel Caesar & Giveon**\n10. **\"Uptown Funk\" - Mark Ronson ft. Bruno Mars**\n11. **\"Titanium\" - David Guetta ft. Sia**\n12. **\"I Gotta Feeling\" - The Black Eyed Peas**\n13. **\"On The Floor\" - Jennifer Lopez ft. Pitbull**\n14. **\"Party Rock Anthem\" - LMFAO ft. Lauren Bennett & GoonRock**\n15. **\"We Found Love\" - Rihanna ft. Calvin Harris**\n\nThese songs span various genres and are known for their catchy beats and danceable rhythms, making them perfect for a club setting. Enjoy the music!",
